imdb.plot outline: The Valley Girl Show draws entrepreneurs -- such as Sheryl Sandberg, Steve Wozniak, Elon Musk and Jessica Alba - out of their comfort zone to generate real, unscripted dialogue with the thought leaders of technology and business. With Draper as the savvy, enthusiastic, knowledgeable host, the audience learns of each entrepreneur's beginnings, follows their process from germ of an idea through the creation of a company, and addresses their current and future goals.
